By BO Staff Writer In the links below (of a podcast and video) Zahid Jadwat in “the Big Discussion” engages Daily Maverick columnist, Ivo Vegter; and Black First Land First (BLF) President, Andile Mngxitama, on the “ Land Debate”. He canvasses what the consequences of Land Expropriation Without Compensation are. The debate is hosted by Salaamedia. Listen: http://bit.ly/2UzJdHZ
